content: solid color version is original model made according to written pattern multicolor version is a modification because it was made with thicker yarn on size h hook only worked 1 row double_crochet 1 row single_crochet for a total of 5 times then edged it with 1 round half_double_crochet to make bunny roll washcloth diagonally bring points together and tie with ribbon to form ears pull remaining point of cloth to front between ears to form nose
